text: Baroness Emerentia von Düben, (24 May, 1669 – 22 March, 1743) was a Swedish lady-in-waiting and favorite of Ulrika Eleonora, Queen of Sweden. Emerentia von Düben was born in Stockholm, Sweden in 1669. She became a lady-in-waiting in 1717. == References == Category:1669 births Category:1743 deaths Category:Swedish nobility
title: Emerentia von Düben
